ivardefs.name: endpoint
ivardefs.desc: Indicates where the message should be routed to.

ivardefs.name: name
ivardefs.desc: Human-readable name for the target system.

ivardefs.name: receiver
ivardefs.desc: Allows data conveyed by a message to be addressed to a particular person or department when routing to a specific application isn't sufficient.

ivardefs.name: target
ivardefs.desc: Identifies the target end system in situations where the initial message transmission is to an intermediary system.

properties.desc: The destination application which the message is intended for.
